snippet.title: Singh Studio
snippet.description:
Hello there, we are Antoni and Rohit Singh , and we make Epic fan trailers for you every week! .
Ever wanted to see Marvel and DC heroes fight? Ever wanted to see Hulk fight Superman, or Batman fight Iron Man, or maybe Deadpool fight Spider-Man? Well, you have come to the right place. Because here, you just might see you wish come true, and heroes fight in Epic "VS" trailer, unite in cool trailer, fight people from Star Wars and much more. On this channel, your craziest dreams as a kid can become an Epic Trailer! 

I'm here to entertain you, and show that Fan trailers are more then just "fake" trailers, I'm here to show you that even trailers that are mash of footage from different movies can still be something that you can enjoy and have fun with!
